  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - The proposal is considered to represent an unacceptable design which would not respect design, proportions or massing of the host site or the surrounding conservation area. The development would erode the characteristic gap between properties and dominate the rear of the property, appearing as though it were a piecemeal addition to the detriment of the wider character and adjoining unit. As such, the proposal would be contrary to Policies DMS1, DMS2 and DMH5 of the DMPD (2016), the Housing SPD (2016), Sutherland Grove Conservation Area Appraisal (2007), Section 72 (1) of the Planning (Listed Buildings and Conservation Areas) Act 1990, Policy HC1c and D3 of the London Plan (2021) and para 199 and 202 of the NPPF (2021)."
